{"tid":2138273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★老年人應否猛鬼？第三波疫情奪30命 港泰群組共9人病逝","createTime":"2020-08-03T13:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T13:03:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f2bbb93fa586de4042362bc3a637ca33df6ff7a","tid":2138273,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"會否成為全港最猛鬼老人院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日本港新冠肺炎疫情肆虐，感染人數連續12日破百，至今才稍回落至80宗確診。第三波疫情更有多間老人院出現群組感染。截至今日（8月3日），疫情爆發至今共造成37人死亡，當中有30人是自7月起的第三波新冠肺炎疫情擴散後感染並離世，而近九成皆是65歲或以上的長者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/506267/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%B3%A2%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%A5%AA30%E5%91%BD-%E8%BF%91%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85-%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%B0%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E5%85%B19%E4%BA%BA%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F506267%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25A5%25AA30%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2585%25B19%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2580%259D&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=9d00e817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/506267/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%B3%A2%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%A5%AA30%E5%91%BD-%E8%BF%91%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85-%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%B0%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E5%85%B19%E4